{"tid":798552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[關囝又柒] PayMe 推出PayCode QR Code 過數","createTime":"2018-08-29T11:20:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T05:16:30.000Z","uid":1159,"like":12,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"72f6e919256abf985f638a5725a2f7c3c5f60c7b","tid":798552,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T11:20:37.000Z","msg":"PayCode 即是您在 PayMe 的 QR 碼。您只需展示您的PayCode，或使用應用程式的內置掃描器、其他 QR 掃描器或手機內的相機掃描 PayCode ，便可進行收款或付款。<br />\n<br />\n將來，當您需分付賬單或向朋友過數時，只需掃描、付款，便可完成支付程序！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/29/181034_6b9f6da4a48645de9a66db3ceb4b1927.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2F181034_6b9f6da4a48645de9a66db3ceb4b1927.png&h=30be5c57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n您可在主頁選擇「付款」或「請求付款」，並點按「PayCode」圖標顯示PayCode，您可掃描或選擇已存取的PayCode，並輸入金額和授權付款便可。<br />\n<br />\nPayCode 亦讓您更輕易地新增朋友 &mdash; 您無需再輸入電話號碼或經 WhatsApp 或手機短訊，傳送款項連結 (雖然您仍可這樣做！）。<br />\n<br />\n您只需有收款人的PayCode，PayMe便可以自動把收款人新增為您的PayMe朋友。"},{"pid":"b7a0f4a9583b7efaad467cab0b4fa89411921039","tid":798552,"uid":198583,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T11:26:49.000Z","msg":"條柒頭關不嬲搞串港瘋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e483d17264befb5e1e83eb31a9f5d6fb59f9512c","tid":798552,"uid":131691,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:04:59.000Z","msg":"唔明<br />\n成圍人入個電話號碼唔係快過逐個排隊scan QR code咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時食飯都會係Phone contact啦"},{"pid":"a11e3a8266ac7d1b40f4a767cbd9d99fac80807e","tid":798552,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:10:52.000Z","msg":"又投共<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74062276f9a6a764efe3a57f0ffefe84483204c5","tid":798552,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:16:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb8149eb95b082d2f9822573fb36e6f282fc0b0e","tid":798552,"uid":1327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e483d17264befb5e1e83eb31a9f5d6fb59f9512c","tid":798552,"uid":131691,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:04:59.000Z","msg":"唔明<br />\n成圍人入個電話號碼唔係快過逐個排隊scan QR code咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時食飯都會係Phone contact啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:18:47.000Z","msg":"明顯 係商業用"},{"pid":"bf6332708b399b9d19b3728bdbfd8d7b39e6eaca","tid":798552,"uid":35587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T04:49:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"925712cbdef8f5353694082189d4f12bc15d54b8","tid":798552,"uid":93958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T05:05:30.000Z","msg":"小商戶用唔錯呀，又唔洗俾電話號碼，又唔需要裝多部POS<br />\n客變相用信用卡俾但商戶唔洗俾交易手續費，雙贏"},{"pid":"d23d41490aa374ab165588de31f197d2fe4b3d03","tid":798552,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T05:10:03.000Z","msg":"重溫關sir精彩發言<br />\n<br />\n話你係支付寶打手你就係，就算你講明係唔撐支付寶都可以讀心知道你係明反暗撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/102347_0e3fb87539dda51fb9f2e35a95e3d328.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F102347_0e3fb87539dda51fb9f2e35a95e3d328.jpg&h=8ba278f1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/30/201135_927c22d53be4c1e95520e5fa4027810e.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F30%2F201135_927c22d53be4c1e95520e5fa4027810e.PNG&h=efc281b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話人係支付寶打手但冇證據，就話有cap圖人地唔認都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NUrrGHZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNUrrGHZ.png&h=cae86714&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但自己開post話其他人五毛個陣全部都有cap圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/472718/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/472718/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n俾Genzo一句收皮，惱羞成怒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qWXjk2r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FqWXjk2r.png&h=abbae7fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼而講出金句，捉毛唔駛講logic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pI9EXLm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FpI9EXLm.png&h=c0f9f56d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開post自稱準備一打二十，但第五頁之後就開始潛水，最後十頁更完全深潛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/q1ik9UL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fq1ik9UL.png&h=5e0abc83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多處言論暴露佢對mobile payment零認識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/104817_c7da2202001ef3739c67954b4c9dbb31.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F104817_c7da2202001ef3739c67954b4c9dbb31.PNG&h=8326d20f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n關愛座hunter 對mobile payment 零認識就唔好出嚟柒啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/513881/page/1?ref=web&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/513881/page/1?ref=web&amp;post=1</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最經典既「用唔等於撐」理論，一路用一路屌就冇問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jZjiEjO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FjZjiEjO.png&h=223ad838&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見拗唔過人就改口話自己唔反qr code，自打嘴巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/17/125325_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F17%2F125325_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=c37f4f22&s={SIZE}\" />[/quote]"},{"pid":"a2d30a8eb10a2bb5250b4ea2c3db161bed6ef8ce","tid":798552,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T05:13:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b764d315e696a353488daa3670987bf72caf775","tid":798552,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T05:16:30.000Z","msg":"想投共？ 仍左袋底未啊"}]}